Entity(@PathVariable Long id)` - Calls `entityService.getById(id)`\n- `GET /api/v1/entities/{id}/display-status` → Returns entity status with display mappings\n\n**POST Endpoints**:\n- `POST /api/v1/entities/query` → `Pagination<Entity> queryFailedEntities(@RequestBody EntityQueryDTO)` - Searches failed entities with pagination\n\n---\n\n#### **EntityService Interface**\n**File**: `/private/tmp/temper-arch/A/ingestion/src/main/java/com/fortinet/nac/ingestion/service/EntityService.java`\n\n**Key Method Signatures**:\n```java\npublic interface EntityService {\n    Entity getById(Long id);\n    Entity getEntity(Long id);\n    Entity getEntity(IngestionRequest req);\n    void save(Entity entity);\n    void saveBatch(Collection<Entity> entityList);\n    Pagination<Entity> queryFailedEntities(EntityQueryDTO req);\n    boolean isProcessingFinished(Long entityId);\n    boolean updateProcessingState(Entity fresh);\n    List<Entity> findStuckEntities(Duration staleThreshold, int maxCount);\n    MarkForReprocessResult markAllForReprocess();\n    List<Long> findTopNIdsByReprocessState(ReprocessState state, int limit);\n    EntityProcessLockInfo findProcessLockInfoById(Long id);\n    boolean claimInitEntityForReprocess(Long id);\n    boolean updateReprocessStateById(Long id, ReprocessState state);\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n#### **EntityServiceImpl Implementation**\n**File**: `/private/tmp/temper-arch/A/ingestion/src/main/java/com/fortinet/nac/ingestion/service/EntityServiceImpl.java`\n\n**Class Signature**:\n```java\n@Slf4j\n@Service\n@RequiredArgsConstructor\npublic class EntityServiceImpl implements EntityService {\n    private final EntityRepository entityRepository;\n    \n    @Qualifier(\"IngestionIdService\")\n    private final IdService idService;\n    \n    private final PlatformTransactionManager transactionManager;\n    private final MeterRegistry meterRegistry;\n```\n\n**Dependency Injection Pattern**: Constructor injection using Lombok's `@RequiredArgsConstructor` with `@Qualifier` annotations for disambiguating beans.\n\n**Transaction Boundaries**:\n```java\n@Transactional(propagation = Propagation.REQUIRES_NEW)\npublic boolean setInterrupted(Long entityId, boolean interrupted) { ... }\n\n@Transactional(propagation = Propagation.REQUIRES_NEW)\npublic boolean updateProcessingState(Entity fresh) { ... }\n\n@Transactional(propagation = Propagation.REQUIRES_NEW)\npublic boolean claimInitEntityForReprocess(Long id) { ... }\n\n@Transactional(propagation = Propagation.REQUIRES_NEW)\npublic boolean updateReprocessStateById(Long id, ReprocessState state) { ... }\n```\n\n**Notable Methods**:\n- `getById(Long id)` - Simple findById using repository\n- `save(Entity entity)` - Generates ID via IdService if null, sets timestamps, delegates to repository\n- `saveBatch(Collection<Entity> entityList)` - Batch save with ID/timestamp generation\n- `markAllForReprocess()` - Complex batch update with independent transaction per batch (REQUIRES_NEW) for fault tolerance\n- Uses `TransactionTemplate` with `PROPAGATION_REQUIRES_NEW` for batch operations\n\n---\n\n#### **EntityRepository**\n**File**: `/private/tmp/temper-arch/A/ingestion/src/main/java/com/fortinet/nac/ingestion/repository/EntityRepository.java`\n\n**Class Signature**:\n```java\npublic interface EntityRepository extends JpaRepository<Entity, Long>, JpaSpecificationExecutor<Entity>\n```\n\n**Key Query Methods**:\n```java\nOptional<Entity> findFirstByTypeAndHostIdentity(EntityType type, String hostIdentity);\nOptional<Entity> findFirstByTypeAndHostIdentityAndUserIdentity(EntityType type, String hostIdentity, String userIdentity);\n\n@Modifying(clearAutomatically = true, flushAutomatically = true)\n@Query(\"update Entity e set e.interrupted = :interrupted, e.updatedAt = :updatedAt where e.id = :id\")\nint updateInterrupted(@Param(\"id\") Long id, @Param(\"interrupted\") boolean interrupted, @Param(\"updatedAt\") Instant updatedAt);\n\n@Query(\"select e from Entity e where e.processingStage <> 'ENF